title: Ep 46: NOOOOOOOOO!
description: The power of NO. Why are we so afraid of saying no to shit we don't want to do? If you're new to saying no how do you get started? Also, Claire Danes' ugly cry face.
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
